Enum MediaDescriptor

    public enum MediaDescriptor
extends Enum<MediaDescriptor>
    Media descriptors. See http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/types.html#h-6.13

    These are typically used with Links.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
